On this #NationalGirlfriendsDay, I’d like to say thanks to YOU! All of you who watched us and stayed with us “through thick and thin.” And to my forever GIRLFRIENDS! The memories run deep and the love runs deeper. @therealgolden47, @itsmejillmarie & @misspersiawhite #girlfriends4life

Watch the full convo here: https://youtu.be/4pSMCwlEF9E

node.text:
In support of Pharrell and his non-profit @blackambitionprize, CHANEL has introduced a mentorship program focused on nurturing emerging Black and Latinx talent and entrepreneurs though access to knowledge and opportunities from industry-leading experts. 
Mentorship is vital to entrepreneurial success, and I’m proud to have participated in “Women Who Lead,” a special panel discussion providing Black Ambition prize contenders with inspiration, insights and career guidance, all told through a women’s lens.  Thank you Pharrell, CHANEL, and @samiranasr. Watch highlights from the conversation here:

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ToN4ziXUHdY 

#blackambition #chanel

node.text:
S MAGAZINE // FALL 2021
In love with this cover! I chatted with @smagazineofficial about @patternbeauty, saying goodbye to Bow, expanding beyond @blackishabc & more. On newsstands September 7! 

“Haircare isn’t binary and should never be. Humans have hair, and however you self-identify, there will always be a need to treat it properly. Our approach is to showcase the natural beauty of Black hair across a wide range of ages and identities.”
